    <stitle>FRONT DRIVE AXLE WHEEL ENDS: FABCO SDA-12 - DISASSEMBLY - INNER AXLE SEAL REMOVAL</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="disassemble" graphiccount="1">
        <title>INNER AXLE SEAL REMOVAL</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Do not remove the seal unless it is to be replaced by a new seal assembly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">The suspension yoke must be off the axle housing before the seal assembly can be removed.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove inner axle shaft.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove suspension yoke from the axle housing by removing eight locknuts and hardened washers
                (refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0201028">Figure 28</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f0201028" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figg02/G0201028.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 28. Removing Suspension Yoke</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Drive the seal from the suspension yoke with a suitable drift.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
